With its unusual shape and faded paintwork, this vehicle could be an old-fashioned toy car.

But in fact, it is one of the first electric cars ever made - and is being put up for auction for more than £20,000.

The rare Pierre Faure was discovered abandoned at a car museum in Chatellerault near Poitiers, France.

